280
00:22:08,240 --> 00:22:12,559
 Sister Mu Dan, could you please meet me? 

281
00:22:16,000 --> 00:22:18,319
 Sister Mu Dan? 

282
00:22:18,319 --> 00:22:21,340
Madam Lian Zhou, what's the matter?

283
00:22:21,340 --> 00:22:27,399
After bathing with flowers last night, I was covered in itchy rashes.

284
00:22:27,399 --> 00:22:31,960
