334
00:27:01,960 --> 00:27:04,140
Don't be arrogant.

335
00:27:05,399 --> 00:27:09,060
Apply it three times a day, and you'll be cured in seven days.

336
00:27:09,520 --> 00:27:13,399
Think about what I've told you today.

337
00:27:13,399 --> 00:27:17,559
If you figure it out, you can come to me anytime.

338
00:27:40,520 --> 00:27:46,860
 I truly don't understand why Young Master Jiang's so devoted to you. 

